            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01JX4G4xzcrUXZ6uXW7gEbef\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I've suggested a few keywords your audience is likely searching for when your ad appears.\\n\\nHow do these sound to you?\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"keywords\\\": [\\n    \\\"meeting scheduling tool for remote teams\\\",\\n    \\\"automatic calendar coordination software\\\",\\n    \\\"find meeting time across time zones\\\",\\n    \\\"team scheduling software\\\",\\n    \\\"meeting scheduler for distributed teams\\\",\\n    \\\"best scheduling tool for global teams\\\",\\n    \\\"eliminate meeting coordination emails\\\",\\n    \\\"calendar sync for multiple time zones\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nThese keywords target:\\n- **High-intent transactional**: \\\"meeting scheduling tool for remote teams\\\", \\\"team scheduling software\\\", \\\"calendar sync for multiple time zones\\\"\\n- **Problem-focused**: \\\"find meeting time across time zones\\\", \\\"eliminate meeting coordination emails\\\"\\n- **Awareness & comparison**: \\\"automatic calendar coordination software\\\", \\\"best scheduling tool for global teams\\\"\\n- **Specific use case**: \\\"meeting scheduler for distributed teams\\\"\\n\\nThey're designed to capture searches from project managers and team leads actively looking for solutions to their scheduling pain points. Ready to move forward with these, or would you like me to adjust the focus?\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":992,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":252,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
